descript.abstract: Drainage Systems (layer) is a symbolized display presentation of the World drainage systems data set. The geographic and attribute data of World drainage systems are symbolized to create the layer. All features are symbolized as a single symbol.
descript.supplinf: For more information about the data set, see its metadata.
